	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Charismatic Authority</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_HELP">
			<Text>How does a man become great? An age-old question that you, comrade, can finally answer for our people.[NEWLINE]So. How did you do it?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Invest {1_YieldCost} in order to generate +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism from Factories.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Your [ICON_DIPLOMAT] Civil Servants generate -2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold but +2 [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism. </Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Invest {1_YieldCost} in order to generate +3 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science from Universities.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Through hard work and manual labour. You think this chiseled exterior doesn't require some kind of upkeep? Everyone should get their hands dirty in our utopian society!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Not by asking my superiors how to do my job! Why do other leaders seem to have infinitely more proficient PR teams? Come back when you've come up with a new poster to distribute to the masses, you sycophant!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_HERO_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Study, endless study. In my time on this planet I must have read near every book ever written! Learning should be the highest aspiration in our society!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
